  "title": "*Patient Service Officer* #HHLT",
  "description": "<p>3 months or longer</p><p>📍 Novena/Orchard</p><p>💰 Salary: Up to $2,800</p><p>🕘 Working Hours: 5.5-day work week (42 hours/week), half-day every Saturday<br /><br /></p><p>Job Scope</p><p>Provide receptionist and front counter duties</p><p>Register patients and ensure accurate clinical data entry</p><p>Coordinate appointments and maintain filing systems</p><p>Perform basic patient care and support clinic operations</p><p>Liaise with insurance companies and assist with payment arrangements</p><p>Handle administrative duties as assigned by Clinic Manager or Doctor</p><p><br /></p><p><br /></p><p>Requirements</p><p>Min O level</p><p>Prior experience as Patient Service Officer preferred</p><p>Medisave submission experience is an advantage</p><p>Comfortable working in a fast-paced clinical environment</p><p>Good communication and interpersonal skills<br /></p><p><br /></p><p>If interested, please email me at biopharma@recruitexpress.com.sg or telegram @alexgohhl</p><p>➖</p><p>Alex Goh Hock Leong</p><p>(CEI.No: R1763413 l Recruit Express Pte Ltd (Healthcare & Life Science) | 99C4599)</p>",
